=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /'blOU/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'blɔʊ/

=== Verb ===

'''to blow''' ([[blew]], [[blown]])

# ''Intransitive'' to produce [[air]] [[flow]]
#* '''''Blow''', winds, and crack your cheeks! rage! '''blow'''!''
# ''Intransitive'' to [[explode]]
# ''Intransitive'' (''slang'') to be very undesirable (see also [[suck]])
#* ''This '''blows'''!''
# ''Transitive'' (often with ''up'') to [[inflate]]
#* '''''blow''' bubbles'', '''''blow''' up a balloon''

